	</div><h1 class="blog_entrytitle">
		Case Of The Lucrative Lure - The Conclusion!
	</h1>
<div class="blogs_entryattribution">
		<a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20100707131434/http://it.toolbox.com/people/chiefmonkey/" class="hoverS">Security Monkey</a>&nbsp;<span class="blogs_postdetails">(Information Security Investigator / CISO)&nbsp;posted&nbsp;6/6/2006 | <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20100707131434/http://it.toolbox.com/blogs/securitymonkey/case-of-the-lucrative-lure-the-conclusion-9742#commentsform" class="hoverS">Comments</a>&nbsp;(9)</span>
