He set her up to hook and reel you in.

and as for it being lucrative, that could refer to 

a) you getting an easy fee if you took the obvious (albiet wrong) conclusion of dana (hence the lure (Dana) was baited with money)

or

b) the fact that this all revolved around the financials of the company.




